name: Beetroot&Beans
description: Fresh fruits and vegetables. Run by the same people behind popular Forest Hill outpost Aga's Little Deli, this lovely, meat-free zero-waste shop has everything from fresh veg and fruit to beans and nuts to alternative milks, as well as gorgeously packaged condiments.
